          "reviewBody": "Excellent school! Highly qualified and caring educators. The priority is always the kids. The educators try to work with individual kids to bring optimal results. The kids get utmost individual attention and the global curriculum helps. Probably one of the very few schools in Coimbatore/tamilnadu where the educators actually listen and also give constructive feedback about the kids.",
