          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hillside Prep is a school with a difference. Their comprehensive curriculum is carefully designed to promote holistic child development.The school's environment(premises to academic staffs to support staffs) is highly conducive to a child's growth, and their commitment to nurturing each child's potential is truly remarkable. The passionate teachers at Hillside Prep pay close attention to every child, which is evident from kids learning trajectory. The students have a genuine fondness for the school, and they offers a wide array of extracurricular activities to further enhance the children's experiences. They offer a thoughtfully crafted menu for both snacks and lunch, ensuring a balance of nutrition while delighting the taste buds of the kids. Additionally, the school's management team is incredibly friendly and approachable making it distinctive indeed...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
