            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Facilities and care is top in class. Very polite and knowledgeable teachers in board. Cambridge education structure. Doctor in-house. Food or snacks served by Sodexo, a French catering company. Any celebration or annual days are professionally conducted and communicated well. Yes, its more than a reasonable fee, but worth the facility provided! Overall, they stand on top in all.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
